            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Anno decimo domini nostri regis <expan><abbr>Guntamun</abbr><ex>di</ex></expan> sub diem II Nonos <note>sic</note> Martias bend<lb break="no" n="2"/>entibus <note>sic</note> Iulius Quintianus et Gilesa uxor eius ex culturis suis Mancianis <lb n="3"/>in fundo Tuletianensis sub dominio <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Gem</abbr><ex>ini</ex></expan> Catullini <expan><abbr>fl</abbr><ex>aminis</ex></expan> in perpetu<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>m</abbr></expan> in locis et <lb n="4"/>vocabulis suis locus qui ap<expan><ex>p</ex><abbr>ellatur</abbr></expan> in Vuresa sus aqua putei massa una in quo s<lb break="no" n="5"/>unt caprufici <note>sic</note> arbore una nomine ERNASSONEV OXVNO odore et fici novellas sex inter adfines <lb n="6"/>eius<surplus>e</surplus>dem loci a marino lateris aquaris bergentisque <note>sic</note> suis ab <expan><abbr>Afri</abbr><ex>co</ex></expan> relicta Luciani <lb n="7"/>a choro Quintianus venditor et ex <expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>ac</abbr></expan> die emit Geminius Felix folles trecentos <lb n="8"/>qua<expan><ex>d</ex><abbr>ranginta</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> quos acceperunt Messius Quintianus et Gilesa uxor eius et sec<lb break="no" n="9"/>um sustullerunt <note>sic</note> coramque <expan><abbr>signatorib</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> nichil <note>sic</note> qu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>esivi</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> ex eodem pretio quiqu<lb break="no" n="10"/>am amplius deveri <note>sic</note> sivi <note>sic</note> respondiderunt <note>sic</note> a pridie quam venderent <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>abuerunt</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>enuerunt</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>ossiderunt</ex></expan> iuri<lb break="no" n="11"/>sque eorum fuerunt et ex <expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>ac</abbr></expan> die in <expan><abbr>no</abbr><ex>mine</ex></expan> Felix em<expan><ex>p</ex><abbr>tore</abbr></expan> suos transtuleru<lb break="no" n="12"/>nt ipsi <expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>eredesve</abbr></expan> eorum in perpetu<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>m</abbr></expan> et si quis de supradictam rem de quo <lb n="13"/>agitur mentionem qu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>estionem</abbr></expan> facere voluerit aut suam esse dixerit <expan><abbr>du</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> evin</ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> ci queperit <note>sic</note> thunc <note>sic</note> davit <note>sic</note> tantum pretium vel alterum tantum vel quanti ae <note>sic</note> res eo <lb n="2"/>tempore valuerit pro evicta rei recte dari sine dolo malo dolus malus abest <lb n="3"/>aberit afuturumque erit stipulatus est Geminius Felix em<expan><ex>p</ex><abbr>tores</abbr></expan> suos <lb n="4"/>sp<expan><ex>o</ex><abbr>p</abbr><ex>on</ex><abbr>d</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>erunt</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> Quintianus et Gilesa uxor eius venditores actum Tuletianos <lb n="5"/>anno et die s<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>pp</abbr><ex>ra</ex></expan> <note>sic</note> <expan><ex>s</ex><abbr>c</abbr><ex>rip</ex><abbr>to</abbr></expan> ego Quadratianus magister petitus a Quintiano et Gilesa <lb n="6"/>uxor <note>sic</note> eius qui litteras nescint signa sua supter <note>sic</note> facientes vendiderunt et omnem <lb n="7"/>pretium acceperunt s<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>g<supplied reason="lost">num</supplied> X Q<supplied reason="lost">u</supplied>in<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied>i<supplied reason="lost">ani</supplied> signum X Gilesa ego P<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>uli<supplied reason="lost">ni</supplied>anus <lb n="8"/>ad <expan><abbr>iussu</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> pattris <note>sic</note> mei Quinti ad hunc instrumentum interfuit ego Urba<lb break="no" n="9"/>n<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>anus ad hunc i<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>strumentu</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> interfui ego Quadratianus ad <expan><abbr>iussu</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> patris <lb n="10"/>m<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>i Ianuari hunc <expan><ex>in</ex><abbr>strumentum</abbr></expan> scribsi <note>sic</note> et subscribsi <note>sic</note> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> i<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>strumentu</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> de caprificu <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>Quintian</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> de Vuresa
            </ab></div></div>
